Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever our High Collar Lady goes, \Ntrouble is sure to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after hearing \NShinobu's tearful story,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact she learned of his grandmother \Ncomplex only made her decision firmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, in order to support \NTamaki's one-sided love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio decided to make a mockery of her \Nlessons in manners to break off her marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will the goddess \Nof fortune smile upon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:50.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,300)\c&HF4EDE5&\pos(720,240)\bord0\blur1\fs50\b1}Episode 6\N{\fs90}A Fleeting Wedding March
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Shinobu's nanny?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You look white as a sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \NHey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady, \Nwhat are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to get all dressed\N up for the big day is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We, as nobles, are taught to \Nmaintain composure at all times...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, we need to talk.\NPlease follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be, Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi, \Nwe humbly beg you to forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been\N tough to raise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You say somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Go, go, go, go, go!\NGet outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who d'ya think you are?! \NYou can't just stop in the middle of the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, if it's a bother,\Nfeel free to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Do you know \Nwho you're talkin' to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! I may not look like much, but I'm Boss Benio's top henchman, the one and only Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in service of Lady Benio, \Nthe future young lady of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio? The young lady \Nof the house? You don't mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from the Ijuuin family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes way, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're tryin' to take the boss away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, Father, \Nno need to be so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is the only promise that I had made\Nto your mother before she passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A white mourning dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. It symbolizes a woman's\N vow to never re-marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are you showing me \Nthis all of a sudden, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother didn't \Nneed to wear this dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're going to marry a soldier—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,if something tragic happens, \Nyou'll have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Never get married again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Am {\i1}I{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}supposed to follow that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you object to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you'd start a new life\Nwith another man if Shinobu died!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, I'm not even married and \Nyou're already acting like I'm a widow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you'll soon become a member of \Nthe Ijuuin family, so you will seldom visit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,About Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk! Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a little of this, some of this, \Nand a little of this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you throwing salt?!\NThis is a luxurious foreign car!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you expect?! \NYou're trying to kidnap the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnap? How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you blabbering about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you heard me!\N You wanna piece of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got a problem, \NUshigoro will take you on any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Salty...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What d'ya expect?! You think you \Ncould go up against the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better remember that taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Givin' up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Exhaust gas... I didn't predict this! {Touge dropped this show here on 21.03.2025 - as it made him want to die}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting married off like this was never in my plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet everyone begs me to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ranmaru, what are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, so, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you're getting married, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfair! It's so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Come on, dummy!\NI won't let myself get married that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back home in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can guarantee you they'll kick me out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ushigorou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, what's that look for...\NStarting a call girl biz? {デリヘル}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Call girl biz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, you don't need to worry that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just apprenticeship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After being evicted, I'll go home very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,if everything goes well, after being back home,\Nyou could be my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... ouch, ow-ow-ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, I'll learn to cook \Nyour favorite grilled chicken,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and all kind of dishes. \NI'll train to become a top-notch chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this conversation's going all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,would you become my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't know how to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it, Nanny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time to head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am, Nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go. See you, Ranmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it looks like she'll be gone forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah! It's so depressing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you sure are annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, if Benio doesn't come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi, I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anchin missed Princess Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,she went crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaoya Oshichi was lovesick, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As was Onatsu Kyouran...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There he goes again,\Nconfusing reality and fiction with one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't be so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be kicked out in no time, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny, look after Father, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady, take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Tamaki, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is a beautiful day, aren't you going outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was walking past here, so I thought of stopping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Such wonderful flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They smell so nicely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any special occasion, madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Shinobu's fiancée is coming over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's Benio...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I mean, is it Lady Hanamura Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right,\Nshe's your classmate, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I can imagine you know her rather well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, we're close friends, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could you tell\Nme how the young lady is like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is going to take,\Nbut I'll act as rude as humanly possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's very kind, also...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:22.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2218AB&\3c&HF2E2DD&\fax-0.312247\fscx109.45\fscy161.38\frz-13.0317\frx-3.1244\fry-7.4698\xbord4.47\ybord6.46\org(956.14,115.57)\pos(964.69,75.23)}Boss Benio's ride
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,wait for me, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and her acquaintances are wonderful people too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's pulling that rickshaw over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my henchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Henchman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Any complaints?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she, of all people, the chosen one to marry the poor Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from this shocked expression...\NI already have a 1-point lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Until marriage, I'll do what it takes for her to be taught properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be cheering for you\Nin your engagement-breaking mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still far from\Nthe Ijuuins' residence, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're already inside the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't this just a forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is part of the estate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the mansion is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I had no idea they were this rich...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your best, for my sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Go-go-go-go! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Benio's faithful henchman... {I don't really understand what she says}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He could be a decisive hand on this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't stand mutts at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, please...\NLook at my face, I'm not suspicious at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If your face is not suspicious, \Nthen I don't know whose is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tamaki!\NEnough laughing, I may be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ijuuins' guard dogs are\Nvery faithful, they bite all strangers without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then, I'm Boss Benio's\Nmost faithful guard, aren't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's negotiate, shall we? \NWhat I'm trying to say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we're like the same pack of dogs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do something about it, Tamaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time \Nthat I've seen Ushigorou so frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shall I escort you to the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady, you may come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya think of the young lad...{I don't know}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I needa young lad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep cool, we're on the same side!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki, please do something, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This man might look threatening,\Nbut he's far from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a wrong impression!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a compliment or an insult?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, these dogs are actually very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd be eager to hear you introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Introducing myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sure, just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me out, hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the great Musashi, I was born\Nin Hanakawado, on the district of Asakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I took an oath of serving Boss Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one and only Ushigorou...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't misjudge me! Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, take it easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shinobu is still\Nbusy and hasn't come back yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so please wait here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, how splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean as a new pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I went a little overboard with this style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal is to act unsavory,\Nand get properly kicked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a cigar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love a box like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you must be my stand-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I work here as a chef assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's almost time for my\Nwedding soon, so I'll have to resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're my stand-in, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The kitchen is right in this direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that you think that\NI look like a chef assistant, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo! I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell are you doing!? \NYou sicken me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange act...  {apparently, the Japanese script has an extra sentence Alucard didn't get in the Italian script (Ziu)}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I sure will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to this misunderstanding, I now feel fully confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so flat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my confidence already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there sure is nobody dwelling there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is what\Nkept company to Shinobu as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she Young Master's future wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have the look of the position!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is such an old mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's this strange sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, the mansion may be old, \Nbut it's not haunted, or is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just another set of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, it's good craftsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Made in Japan" armors can speak, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it moves its eyes, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's see if it's ticklish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on... \NStop! It tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's like the thing's alive. \NI wonder if it's part of the service.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, enough games! {dunno}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to teach you a lesson. Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady is about to get\Nacquainted with a rusty lance...{Idk I don't get it so I put it by feel, the narrator isn't even speaking in the ITA version, they made characters speak lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of foe wields it?{敵もさるもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,An armored warrior appears before Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:23:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but the man under the helmet \Nis none other than Count Ijuuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, an intrepid Samurai of Satsuma! {I'm sorry this part is just difficult}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.99,0:23:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He dislikes Benio from the get-go. {or something like this, he says はじめの出会いから[わるか？]}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As a problem can hide another, the High Collar-style\Nengagement-breaking mission takes on water!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady{\i0}:\N"Count, Forgive Me"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
